:markdown-it
  The main menu is the primary navigation on large viewports.
  It is prominently placed in the
  [Header Component](/components/header.html "Header Component").
  
  The component displays the first level of your navigation.
  Further levels are displayed on hover or touch, where they
  appear in an overlay residing directly under the main menu.
  
aside.callout
  h2.callout__heading Not mobile-ready!
  :markdown-it
    Because of the large complexity of this component, there
    is no mobile version of the *main menu component*. Navigation on
    small viewports is instead handled using the
    [Mobile Menu Component](/components/mobile-menu.html "Mobile Menu Component").

