          :markdown-it
            If you omit the `data-menu="main"` attribute, the
            menu won't get any functionality.
            
            In order to add
            the missing functionality programmatically, simply initialize the
            `$().mainMenu()` plugin.
            
            ```js
            var menu = $("[data-menu='main']")
            
            // initialize the plugin
            menu.mainMenu()
            ```

